    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a definitive analog performance machine. At its heart is the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS to produce a high-strung 333 hp with an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the preferred 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M-variable differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearing service has been completed\u2014critical preventative measures for this chassis. The suspension remains taut, featuring a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear configuration that delivers precise turn-in and exceptional chassis balance. While the exterior and interior show honest wear consistent with a well-loved driver, the mechanical vitals are sharp, and the throttle response remains visceral. It is a mechanically robust specimen ready for the canyon roads.",
      "price": 34500.0,
