    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior features a deep midnight blue metallic finish that still holds a brilliant shine, showing only minor road peppering on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful ownership. The body is straight with no history of accidents or major dents. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with premium charcoal leather upholstery; the seats are firm and supportive, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that starts instantly. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes were recently inspected and cleared for many more miles. This is a dependable, well-presented car that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
